longBusinessSummary: China Uptown Group Company Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the property development and raw sugar trading businesses in the People's Republic of China. It operates through Property Development and Investment; and Trading of Raw Cane Sugar segments. The company develops and sells office premises, retail stores, commercial, residential properties, and car parking spaces, as well as invests in properties. It also trades in raw cane sugar; and supplies basic electronic component materials and products. In addition, the company supplies natural resources, such as iron ore and coal, as well as commodities to the industrial corporations. China Uptown Group Company Limited is headquartered in Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong.
